name: Kiwi the Derpit
description:
Kiwi is flying in the sky.
Kiwi is galaxies far high.
He's gone to outer space...
...To ascend beyond our globe.
He's got a 6-pack paddy-whack, give a dog a bone:
"Now listen here, Mr. Derpit... You've been really patient waiting for these slow cooked meatballs; I think you deserve having your face sat on before supper."
